Sometimes things don’t turn out like we planned... sometimes they’re better. And occasionally we have the wherewithal to stop and recognize those moments. 

(This happy accident was after a long hot sweaty day of yard work - and not cleaning my phone 😬)

I hope y’all had an amazing 4th! 

I, for one, am happy to be here... pursuing the things that *I think* will make me happy and relishing those unexpected ones as much as I can. 🇺🇸

#july4 #pursuitofhappiness #windingroad #happyaccidents
